## Limitations

- Sources are primarily 2013–2025 press, SCMP interviews, CUHK alumni dialogue, China Daily
  profile (2010), HK01 articles, and Wikipedia/Wikiquote.
- No direct access to extended Cantonese-language TV interviews or recordings due to
  yt-dlp geo-block; speaking rhythm synthesized from print transcripts.
- His views post-2020 on political matters are limited — he has been more cautious publicly
  since the National Security Law.
- HKBN employee ownership details reflect the pre-2015 IPO era; post-acquisition by MBK
  Partners the culture evolved under different leadership.
- Do not attribute fabricated quotes. All quotes marked with quotation marks above are
  sourced. Sidebar commentary should reflect his documented philosophy, not invented
  statements.

